============================================================
MATRIZ DE PROBABILIDADES
============================================================

P(Home=a) = (e^-λ_home * λ_home^a) / a!
P(Away=b) = (e^-λ_away * λ_away^b) / b!

P(a,b) = P(Home=a) * P(Away=b)

Probabilidades:
- Victoria local → a > b
- Empate → a = b
- Victoria visitante → a < b

============================================================
AJUSTE DIXON-COLES
============================================================

P_ajustada = P_Poisson * τ(a,b,λ_home,λ_away,ρ)

Corrige:
- 0-0
- 1-0
- 0-1
- 1-1

============================================================
AJUSTE CONTEXTO COMPETITIVO
============================================================

λ_home_final = λ_home_base * factor_contexto_home
λ_away_final = λ_away_base * factor_contexto_away

factor_contexto:
- 1.10 → mayor ataque
- 1.00 → neutro
- 0.90 → menor ataque

